MsgEn:
Reduce your enemy and make the most of yourself; 
That's the essence.
Winning and losing, life and death, are all just the result of what comes with it.

I consider myself the captain's right-hand man;
No matter who comes back or leaves,
That will never change.

Arisen, I had you take a look at it the other day;
It's an "old well under a lighthouse",
You see the sealed door at the back?

There are no signs of movement so far, but
if they start to approach the village,
there is sure to be trouble.

